    "120675583": {
      "title": "Recursion formulas for the Lie integral",
      "abstract": "Abstract An explicit definition is given of a non-linear integral which is termed the Lie integral . This integral is defined for Lie algebra valued functions in terms of the representations of the algebra. Various properties of the integral are investigated, and applications are given to differential equations. Applications to differential geometry will be given elsewhere."
